{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471320/extras/Description_Banner__1.png?t=1738251903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a mansion trapped beyond time, plagued by the unknown\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A weakened one, left to perish, becomes possessed by their wrath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471320/extras/Description_Banner__2.png?t=1738251903\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The chains that once bound you are now your greatest weapon. Wield them to navigate the unfathomable halls of this labyrinthine structure. With many secrets to uncover and no guidance but the echoes of the past, fight your way through the mansion\u2019s shifting depths and unravel the truth buried within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3471320/extras/Description_Banner__3.png?t=1738251903\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master satisfying 3D platforming... Use your heavy chain to swing, jump, and propel yourself through the world, offering a unique and rewarding movement experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a 3D Metroidvania... Discover a vast, interconnected world full of secrets as you unlock new abilities and navigate challenging areas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel the mansion\u2019s mysteries... Delve into a mansion packed with hidden shortcuts and secrets, each area offering a distinct atmosphere and mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in dynamic combat... Face off against unique enemies, using your chain both as a weapon and a tool to overcome the mansion\u2019s dangers.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store